 dioxide. Your cells produce too much lactic acid in compensation and that drives the respiratory

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:13.480
 system inappropriately and makes you lose a little bit of carbon dioxide that you are

00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:20.480
 producing. Hypothyroidism is one of the basic things driving hyperventilation. There tends

00:08:24.960 --> 00:08:31.960
