00:10:39.280 --> 00:10:49.220
 risk of asthma and that's partly because it increases endotoxin absorption from the

00:10:49.220 --> 00:10:59.400
 intestine and circulation in the bloodstream and partly because estrogen lowers the thyroid

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:06.400
 function. All of which tend to lower the production of carbon dioxide leading to a relative hyperventilation

00:11:06.400 --> 00:11:15.460
 and alkalosis which helps to excite the inflammation and contraction in the bronchial system.

